com.vmware.vcenter.vm.guest.filesystem

Interface FilesTypes

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Files
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FilesStub

    public interface FilesTypes
    The Files interface provides methods to manage the files in the guest filesystem. This interface was added in vSphere API 7.0.2.0.
